Returns: The quest that was accepted. This will be null if the accept operation did not succeed.

ClassDesc: Result delivered when accepting a quest. Possible status codes include: @B_com#google#android#gms#games#GamesStatusCodes#STATUS_OK_E@ if the request was successful and the quest is updated after accepting. @B_com#google#android#gms#games#GamesStatusCodes#STATUS_NETWORK_ERROR_NO_DATA_E@ if the device was unable to retrieve any data from the network and has no data cached locally. @B_com#google#android#gms#games#GamesStatusCodes#STATUS_INTERNAL_ERROR_E@ if an unexpected error occurred in the service.
